race.comment: EXCELOQUENT (13) returned in fine fashion with a dominant win over this course and distance and will have derived a stack of confidence from that outing. Looks the one who will be playing a major role in the outcome. SAGA'S GIRL (6) has won two of three this campaign and maps well from gate three. Has to be included in calculations. FAST FUSION (3) draws the inside marble and gets a bunch of weight off with the 3kg claim. Top-three prospects on best figures. DUNE AND DUSTED (1) goes well for hoop Vitler and may earn some minor money. A TOUCH FROM FAYT (14) rounds out the selections in a race decimated by scratchings.
